# Frame sequence drop-in folder
#
# Ahmed's creative pipeline outputs here:
#   Gemini → Wisk → Flow → ffmpeg extract → frame-001.jpg .. frame-030.jpg
#
# Expected files:
#   /public/frames/frame-001.jpg
#   /public/frames/frame-002.jpg
#   ...
#   /public/frames/frame-030.jpg
#
# Recommended specs:
#   - JPG, quality ~80
#   - 1920x1080 (or 1280x720 mobile)
#   - ~50-80KB each, ~1.5-2.4MB total
#
# Until these exist, components/interactive/FrameSequence.tsx falls back
# to components/interactive/PlaceholderHand.tsx — an SVG schematic that
# still responds to scroll.
